{"type": "article", "id": 16102, "title": "Fujifilm Instax Wide", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-15T06:20:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 85, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135558cefVGnmSDOx3pgtz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是富士推出的新系列，比 Fujifilm Instax Mini 大两倍， 配备 90mm 的镜头和 3 种拍摄模式：Auto、长曝及 1/30 秒固定快门模式，其他功能都保留经典配置。例外在镜头盖，通常没有用的镜头盖在这里变成了快门遥控，手动下拉是非常原始传统的体验。即日将在网上预售，其中蓝绿配色为经典款。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143501osKFmwJBW0PMDZEi.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143501ULivxd1WGon9ZHrJ.gif\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143502iCrgumBzR6MkbU1X.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143503f3xWyvrd29iBeHbo.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}